\subsection{Elf}

An elf is a slim agile humanoid, who frequents wooded areas.

\textbf{Traits:} Elves are virtually immortal and generally take the
long term view. They are insular, indifferent to others and tend to be
traditional.  Elves are great respecters of nature and learning. Their
Elders are repositories of great wisdom while elvish youth are
enthusiastic merry makers. Elven warriors favour bow weapons and
disdain metal armour. Members of other races generally find elves
d575 1
