Average Life Span: Circa 10,000 years \\
\end{flushleft}

\subsection{Halfling}

A halfling is a short, cheerful humanoid, who will be an active
participant in village life.

\textbf{Traits:} Halflings appreciate the good life more than most; a
successful halfling will arrange a schedule of much sleep, good food,
and relaxed study or conversation. Halfling are shy around other races
preferring to merge into the background.  Amongst themselves they are
a friendly folk, who form into small communities where everyone knows
everyone else's business. While Halflings take their social
responsibilities seriously, they are renowned for their practical
jokes and light fingers. Halflings are noted for their tough, hairy
feet and usually go barefoot. Halflings avoid the rigours of military
life but when forced to defend themselves they favour small weapons.
