\subsection{Hill Giant}

A hill giant is a huge, coarse featured humanoid, who has no patience
for laborious learning.

\textbf{Traits:} Giants are lusty types, preferring nothing better
than to go through life brawling, drinking, and wenching. They tend to
gather together in a clan arrangement, building huge halls (or
