\textbf{Traits:}
Giants are lusty types, preferring nothing better than to go through
life brawling, drinking, and wenching.  They tend to gather together
in a clan arrangement, building huge halls (or steadings) in
out-of-the-way locations.  They are not overly intelligent, and resent
humans and elves particularly.  Giants enjoy riddling and bartering.
Giant warriors favour the club and sword (scaled to their size).
