\subsubsection{A human is a standard humanoid, who frequents most areas
and climes.}
d730 24
a753 9
\textbf{Traits:}
Humans have a great diversity of cultures and languages,
and sub-racial traits, such as hair and eye colour or skin tone.
They inhabit and thrive in most environments, and may even be
found in climates far outside their optimums.

\textbf{Special Abilities:}
Human characters receive no special abilities or modifiers to their
characteristics due to their race.
d756 2
