\textbf{Traits:}
Orcs are a cruel, violent folk, liking nothing better than to rape and
pillage.  Individually, orcs are a cowardly lot, but a charismatic
leader can turn a band of orcs into a conquering horde.  Orc enjoy the
sensual pleasures of life, and reduce their already short life span
through hard living.  Orc warriors favour the scimitar.  Orcs are
considered unattractive by other humanoid races.
d880 1
d888 7
